query:
INSERT INTO polling_stations (
            committee_session_id,
            id_prev_session,
            name,
            number,
            number_of_voters,
            polling_station_type,
            address,
            postal_code,
            locality
        )
        SELECT
            ? AS committee_session_id,
            id AS id_prev_session,
            name,
            number,
            number_of_voters,
            polling_station_type,
            address,
            postal_code,
            locality
        FROM polling_stations
        WHERE committee_session_id = ?
